measurements.description: Eighty-four flowers and 48 buds on 14 up to 3.1 cm inflorescences; 16-cm wide by 14-cm tall leafless plant growing on six-cm x ten-cm compressed cork; stellate flowers translucent white; sepals lanceolate, light green vein centrally; petals ovate, slightly porrect; lip flat, widely ovate, spur seven mm long; column white, anther cap yellow; substance light; texture crystalline; also awarded AM #20255289.
